title: Vegetarian Food Stall
description: This food stall offers vegetarian sandwiches and sticky rice, and the flavors taste good not bland. Owners disciples of Supreme Master Ching Hai. It's in District 5 and close to District 1, right off Tran Hung Dao. Huynh Man Dat is the street located right after Le Hong Phong if you are coming from District 1.
